flowchart TD
    START([Screening results available for student]) --> A

    A[Teacher views screening results\nLD scores & SHAP explanation] --> B
    B[Teacher browses Activity Catalog\nGET /activities/catalog?ld_type=...] --> C
    C[Teacher selects activities\nbased on flagged LD domains] --> D
    D[POST /activities/assign\nstudent_id + activity_keys] --> E
    E[System creates StudentActivityAssignment records\nassigned_by = teacher, is_active = true] --> F

    F([Student is notified / logs in]) --> G

    G[Student login\nPOST /auth/student-login\nusername + password] --> H{Valid\ncredentials?}
    H -- No --> ERR([Error: Wrong username or password])
    H -- Yes --> I[JWT token issued\nrole = student]

    I --> J[GET /activities/my-activities\nFetch assigned active activities] --> K

    K{Activities\nassigned?}
    K -- No --> WAIT([No activities yet — check later])
    K -- Yes --> L

    L[Student selects an activity\nViews instructions + interactive content] --> M
    M[Student completes activity\nAnswers / interactions recorded] --> N

    N[POST /activities/attempt\nscore + time_taken_seconds] --> O
    O[System calculates XP earned\nattempt_number incremented] --> P
    P[Save StudentProgress record to DB\nactivity_key, score, time, attempt_number] --> Q

    Q{Student wants\nanother attempt?}
    Q -- Yes --> L
    Q -- No --> R

    R[Student views own progress\nGET /activities/my-progress] --> S([Progress summary displayed\nscores per activity over time])

    S --> T[Teacher / Parent views progress\nGET /dashboard/students] --> U([Student card updated\nwith latest activity scores])
